y to put everything into a company. I&#8217;m not willing to do that anymor=
e. I&#8217;m constantly turning down in-person meetings, dinners, and other=
 time-consuming things that would probably be good for my career but would =
mean less time with Dev and Puja. At least when the baby is little, I think=
