p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 1em 0;">It&#8217;s all gone into hyperdrive recently, though. Even thoug=
h he&#8217;s only one, you can already tell that he&#8217;s kind and funny =
