says mama and dada like he knows what he&#8217;s talking about. He&#8217;s =
like a little grownup in a baby body.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Even now, just a ye=
